TI  - A weighted QoS aware multipath routing process in Mobile Ad hoc networks
PY  - 2013
T2  - Proceedings - IEEE Symposium on Computers and Communications
C7  - 6754969
SP  - 336
EP  - 341
DO  - 10.1109/ISCC.2013.6754969
